==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Explicitly
<hw>Ex*plic"it*ly</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>adv.</pos> <def>In an explicit
manner; clearly; plainly; without disguise or reservation of meaning;
not by inference or implication; <as>as, he <ex>explicitly</ex> avows
his intention</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Explicitness</ent>⟦br⟧
